Write a function that is able to transform a string in a few different ways:
    1. make a string be all lowercase
    2. MAKE A STRING BE ALL UPPERCASE
    3. Make A String Have Capital Letters On Every New Word
    4. MoCk SoMeOnE bY dOiNg SoMeThInG lIkE tHiS
    5. Come up with another new way to transform a given string.